Syntax: caravan <city>

Boards a departing caravan wagon at the Caravan Square in Midgaard and
travels directly to another city's caravan quarter.

Available destinations:
  Kiess    - The forest-edge trade hub on Roc Road
  Kowloon  - The delta port city to the south
  Mafdet   - The desert harbor city
  Rakuen   - The eastern Canopy Compact city

Requirements:
  - You must be standing at the Caravan Square in Midgaard (the central
    plaza of Midgaard's caravan quarter).
  - You must have completed the cartographic survey quest for the target
    city. Each city's postmaster in Midgaard offers a city district survey
    commission; completing and turning in that quest records your knowledge
    of the city's layout in the caravan routing records.
  - You cannot board a caravan while engaged in combat.

The caravan master consults the transit authority's navigation records
before accepting passengers. Without a completed survey on file, the
routing office cannot confirm safe arrival, and passage is refused.

Partial city names are accepted (e.g. 'caravan kow' for Kowloon).

See also: recall, quest
